{"tid":2208981,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"吉列粟米斑塊飯","createTime":"2020-09-19T10:08:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T05:05:33.000Z","uid":239860,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7ce04a90454f2c121b7394a6e6b4c58045fe24dd","tid":2208981,"uid":239860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T10:08:33.000Z","msg":"今次整左吉列粟米班塊飯，又係好易整，炸兩炸，煮兩煮就搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有興趣可以睇下條片，記得訂閱我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stretching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mvmj8D8oWEo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fmvmj8D8oWEo&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCvDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=0b38522f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mvmj8D8oWEo</a><br />\n<br />\n製成品<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SO90GpP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSO90GpP.jpg&h=ec207543&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首先攞啲青衣柳出黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iq1qSwE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fiq1qSwE.jpg&h=07ebc936&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後切片<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cSO8Qiq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcSO8Qiq.jpg&h=07f08cca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再上粉炸<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g1gygYA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg1gygYA.jpg&h=b719663d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n整埋個粟米汁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/shNhJDK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FshNhJDK.jpg&h=da14233f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁就完成啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鍾意嘅可以分上<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e2P4oDY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe2P4oDY.jpg&h=77d68a71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咪又簡單又快呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c28ebd482b60acf6c8b1647f43c4bf2f2182cb","tid":2208981,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T10:08:44.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"41b723d93e7f0bcbf486affa3541bd4ff49c68fa","tid":2208981,"uid":212623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T10:09:01.000Z","msg":"不錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a4a71767214a0cd3ca49f45f817b9f7d43cde1a","tid":2208981,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T10:09:37.000Z","msg":"今次好快手 而家睇片先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1156cdecb1b98795b5404b1410d86a8f2d42dff5","tid":2208981,"uid":131631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T10:09:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69cc65cde43e699c89b9b5ef5166c8b21bab9569","tid":2208981,"uid":239860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47c28ebd482b60acf6c8b1647f43c4bf2f2182cb","tid":2208981,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T10:08:44.000Z","msg":"1"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T10:09:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6fed4c6752f4fdd9f69ef1bfe5b4c4ee5680e05","tid":2208981,"uid":239860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41b723d93e7f0bcbf486affa3541bd4ff49c68fa","tid":2208981,"uid":212623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T10:09:01.000Z","msg":"不錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T10:10:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58df2812d741f39ad1303bd02d6d6eafd1a44b01","tid":2208981,"uid":239860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"